{"tid":1808871,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］新嘅遊行點人數方法","createTime":"2020-01-02T15:56:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T12:56:29.000Z","uid":303520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"828e21bd58b7c6a1e3c607ae71dfa77a9b58d6a9","tid":1808871,"uid":303520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T15:56:27.000Z","msg":"啱啱過左民陣元旦大遊行 文宣一直都強調一定要經維園入 雖然有好多乖寶寶都肯喺維園乾等幾粒鐘甚至琴晚有d人係未起步已經被解散 同時亦都有好多人都係頂唔順去左插隊/中間路線加入 其實單靠喺維園點人數真係唔係辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我自己就諗左一個方法唔知work唔work 擺喺度拋磚引玉啦：<br />\n用<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">QR Code</span></span>黎收集數據work唔work呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺起點終點同埋遊行路線中間可能每隔100米/喺天橋上面就掛幾個大嘅QR Code比人scan 每機淨係可以scan一次 個QR Code過左果一日就無效 好似返工打卡咁 只不過佢唔會留任何痕跡喺你嘅電話上面 淨係佢單方面收集數據 遊行終止之後qr code同埋數據就會註銷 <br />\n咁樣應該對人流控制會比較有利？不過私隱安全都係存疑嘅...<br />\n大家會唔會有其他方法點遊行人數？"},{"pid":"dd4ad43e0ac6f1a5b79f7f8d8f4da569cb508c27","tid":1808871,"uid":29625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T16:01:28.000Z","msg":"上撚到網咩阿哥"},{"pid":"656894d3ae2c95cb10c21dd010189f2a4d0fb6fd","tid":1808871,"uid":19386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T16:10:45.000Z","msg":"唔work，個QR code share左出街，我係屋企都scan到"},{"pid":"f149092e6a791bbf71f045039a6972db6b8259e0","tid":1808871,"uid":296664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd4ad43e0ac6f1a5b79f7f8d8f4da569cb508c27","tid":1808871,"uid":29625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T16:01:28.000Z","msg":"上撚到網咩阿哥"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T16:15:51.000Z","msg":"仲有好多問題 例如公信力<br />\nQR code可以影低share出去<br />\n<br />\n不過唔駛咁惡嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用高空航拍嘅錄象去估算係其中一個方法<br />\n至少estimate最高峰時期嗰刻嘅人數可以幾準確"},{"pid":"010c8235b8d3d75ab1df7b1bc5b65f7a8fd7ac30","tid":1808871,"uid":303520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd4ad43e0ac6f1a5b79f7f8d8f4da569cb508c27","tid":1808871,"uid":29625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T16:01:28.000Z","msg":"上撚到網咩阿哥"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T06:08:16.000Z","msg":"我拋磚引玉咋師兄 你有無其他好d嘅idea<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2020a087ce8026c843887724b8637a70a43763c","tid":1808871,"uid":303520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"656894d3ae2c95cb10c21dd010189f2a4d0fb6fd","tid":1808871,"uid":19386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T16:10:45.000Z","msg":"唔work，個QR code share左出街，我係屋企都scan到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T06:09:58.000Z","msg":"啱啊其實呢個係其中一個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打卡佬影完放上ig就玩完了"},{"pid":"80f74f5ae7f144a4520cb9a7dcb3ee96144eb9bd","tid":1808871,"uid":303520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f149092e6a791bbf71f045039a6972db6b8259e0","tid":1808871,"uid":296664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd4ad43e0ac6f1a5b79f7f8d8f4da569cb508c27","tid":1808871,"uid":29625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T16:01:28.000Z","msg":"上撚到網咩阿哥"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T16:15:51.000Z","msg":"仲有好多問題 例如公信力<br />\nQR code可以影低share出去<br />\n<br />\n不過唔駛咁惡嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用高空航拍嘅錄象去估算係其中一個方法<br />\n至少estimate最高峰時期嗰刻嘅人數可以幾準確"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T06:11:01.000Z","msg":"其實呢個方法幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  可惜我p牌仔推唔到你"},{"pid":"da3f34f7694de186e7afd58d4006cb8d78cd2368","tid":1808871,"uid":274999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T09:32:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www1.hkej.com/dailynews/article/id/2219510/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.hkej.com%2Fdailynews%2Farticle%2Fid%2F2219510%2F&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPjQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=a0366149\" target=\"_blank\">https://www1.hkej.com/dailynews/article/id/2219510/</a><br />\n人數=密度&times;面積&times;時間<br />\n<br />\n我覺得分幾個checkpoint<br />\n當起點到終點中間有兩個checkpoint啦, 當隊頭出發每經過一個cp就由高空向起點方向影一張相直至到終點, 而當隊頭經個CP1 就會有人通知起點帶D巨型橫額出發(下稱新隊頭), 當第一個新隊頭經過CP1 , 起點就再開一隊新隊頭出去, 直至起點所有人已經出發完畢<br />\n<br />\n咁用 密度&times;面積既方法將所有隊頭既最高人數路段加晒起黎, 應該就得到最大人數.<br />\n假設依家開左3個隊頭<br />\n 起點   CP1   CP2   終點<br />\n隊頭1   5K       6K     5K<br />\n隊頭2   8K       7K      7K<br />\n隊頭3   7K        8K     9K<br />\n<br />\n6+7+9=21K<br />\n<br />\n我冇讀過書唔識野亂咁9UP但屌還屌唔好屌老母"},{"pid":"9aa4111c24644fd0955cc5db21e5099cf28521bf","tid":1808871,"uid":303520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da3f34f7694de186e7afd58d4006cb8d78cd2368","tid":1808871,"uid":274999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T09:32:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www1.hkej.com/dailynews/article/id/2219510/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.hkej.com%2Fdailynews%2Farticle%2Fid%2F2219510%2F&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPjQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=a0366149\" target=\"_blank\">https://www1.hkej.com/dailynews/article/id/2219510/</a><br />\n人數=密度&times;面積&times;時間<br />\n<br />\n我覺得分幾個checkpoint<br />\n當起點到終點中間有兩個checkpoint啦, 當隊頭出發每經過一個cp就由高空向起點方向影一張相直至到終點, 而當隊頭經個CP1 就會有人通知起點帶D巨型橫額出發(下稱新隊頭), 當第一個新隊頭經過CP1 , 起點就再開一隊新隊頭出去, 直至起點所有人已經出發完畢<br />\n<br />\n咁用 密度&times;面積既方法將所有隊頭既最高人數路段加晒起黎, 應該就得到最大人數.<br />\n假設依家開左3個隊頭<br />\n 起點   CP1   CP2   終點<br />\n隊頭1   5K       6K     5K<br />\n隊頭2   8K       7K      7K<br />\n隊頭3   7K        8K     9K<br />\n<br />\n6+7+9=21K<br />\n<br />\n我冇讀過書唔識野亂咁9UP但屌還屌唔好屌老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T12:56:29.000Z","msg":"好似好勁咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過我睇唔明 我先係冇讀過書果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}